Example: Just Doubles, Please

oddEven &lt;- function(x){
  if (!is.double(x)){
    stop("Value is not of a double type.")
  }
  if (x %% 2 == 0){
    print("odd")
  } else {
    print("even")
  }
}
oddEven("apple")

Error in `oddEven()`:
! Value is not of a double type.

